<h1>The Web is a Tough Place - Select the Right &lt;div&gt; and Conquer?</p>
<p>The game is simple, start the game pick any two elements on any page and watch them fight to the death. Make any webpage your plaything! </p>

<h1>Why &lt;div&gt;&amp;conquer?</h1>
<p>Div and conquer is a silly game made by a student trying to push what he could do with JQuery. The original idea was to make a webpage into a gameboard, inspired by the game of thrones opening animations, where flat landscapes build into 3D fortresses. I wanted to do the same thing with any webpage you might decide needs some life, and then be able tto battle between these elements. A week is not a long time to do this, but that was all we had, so somewhere along the way game-of-doms changed course and became more of a cage match for page elements. Oh well.</p>
